nl.helixsoft.recordstream

Interface NextUntilNull<T>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractRecordStream, Adjuster, Cast, ChunkedRecordStream, Filter, HssfRecordStream, Join, Melt, MemoryRecordStream, Reducer, ResultSetRecordStream, TsvRecordStream, XssfRecordStream

    public interface NextUntilNull<T>
    Helper interface for stream-like objects. Call getNext() repeatedly until null is returned. Null indicates the end of stream. Especially useful in combination with IteratorHelper
